snippet.title: BLADESONG | Announcing the THIRD PLAYTEST! June 17–30 on Steam
snippet.description:
Request Access on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2305640/Bladesong/
Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/bladesong

The next Playtest will go live on June 17! Request Access now on Steam to join ⚔️
If you have already particpated in any previous Playtest, the game is still in your Steam library and will automatically be unlocked on the starting date.
